### Crear usuario
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "jperez",
    "email": "jperez@mednova.com",
    "initialPassword": "Temporal123!",
    "thirdPartyId": 10
}

###

### Crear usuario sin tercero vinculado
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "mlopez",
    "email": "mlopez@mednova.com",
    "initialPassword": "Temporal456!"
}

###

### Obtener usuario por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar usuarios (sin búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "u.nombre_usuario",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar usuarios (con búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "perez",
    "order_by": "u.nombre_usuario",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar usuario
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "jperez.nuevo@mednova.com",
    "thirdPartyId": 10
}

###

### Activar / Inactivar usuario (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/1/toggle-active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Bloquear / Desbloquear usuario (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/1/toggle-blocked HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Resetear contraseña de usuario
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/users/1/reset-password HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newPassword": "NuevaClave789!"
}

